{"tid":843203,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴4個字拒採訪：你想我死？","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T05:05:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d454559e5184879880af8aab05d511ea9d81ac","tid":843203,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2NKyO7fI0FiLhX2dfX1LHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d8de731d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯將帥不和傳聞繼續發酵，主角之一的保羅普巴冷然用4個字，拒絕就此事受訪。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯上周末敗走倫敦，以1:3受挫於韋斯咸，在下半場被換走的保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）離開時自是一臉不悅，當他在訪問區被記者截停，對方要求進行訪問時，他回應：「你想我死（You want me dead）？」<br />\n<br />\n普巴被指與摩連奴的關係處於前所未有的低點，先是有傳普巴批評摩佬的戰術，然後是摩佬褫奪其副隊長職位，而兩人上周中在訓練場怒目相向，之後候車出發前往倫敦準備鬥韋斯咸時，企到離行離列，並沒交流。<br />\n<br />\n有傳普巴可能在來年1月轉會窗重開後，重返祖雲達斯或轉投巴塞隆拿。至於英國《太陽報》較早前指，普巴將於下月透過經理人與曼聯會方傾談前程。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"9df8eee4ddf0b3cf84f3018d175c25904d951452","tid":843203,"uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3ad09d1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e8392f872fd78612b9d2cd2540d8d712ee0c466","tid":843203,"uid":95991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3813b83c1c52b8d4dbbb43adfe09cbb2904649","tid":843203,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"居然識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc4e91f532d4950d019aa6b4f3b96d75d8c41ae","tid":843203,"uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"20